File::Find::Rule::DirectoryEmpty - find empty directories recursively
=====================================================================


	use File::Find::Rule::DirectoryEmpty;
   	
	my @emptydirs = File::Find::Rule->directoryempty->in('/home/myself');
   

INSTALLATION

perl Makefile.PL
make test
make install

DEPENDENCIES

   Cwd
   File::Find::Rule
   Test::Simple

